FIFO
    2bit
        read
        write
        nothing

    3 bit P1 function
        incr read
        zero read
        incr write
        zero write
        nothing

    3 bit P2 function
        incr read
        zero read
        incr write
        zero write
        nothing

    1bit
        change player
        nothing

